snippet.title: Milly Marathon Update - Necrolepsy
snippet.description:
Store page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/985590

Lira thought she was done with Lina Labyrinth's boss rush mode, but it turns out an entire new adventure awaits in Milly Marathon, an enemy gauntlet where you go room-to-room and fight your way through hordes of enemies!
